Titolo: Motocross Madness 2

Anno: 2000

Descrizione: Motocross Madness 2 is a motocross racing video game that was developed by Rainbow Studios and published by Microsoft Games.This sequel to 1998's Motocross Madness was released on May 26, 2000, with improved graphics, which included better textures and many landscape objects like trees, road signs and caravans. It has over 40 tracks in 6 event types, over 50,000 3D objects and a new career mode. Players as well as bikes are easily customized. Motocross Madness also supports network play over a LAN environment and, until June 19, 2006, multiplayer gameplay through the MSN Gaming Network.